{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ca4594d10d","title":"在中央关于三反中处理科学家、学者的问题的指示稿上加写的话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"14df879c61","index":0,"year":1952,"month":3,"day":7,"articleId":"ca4594d10d"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"bebd03e3a6","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"ca4594d10d","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"毛泽东的这句话，是在审阅中共中央关于三反斗争中如何处理科学家、学者的问题的指示稿时加写的。指示稿说：“三反斗争中对于这类有用的专门科学家和学者的处理，应该以思想改造为主，对于解放以前有贪污行为者，均作为思想问题来解决。对于解放以后有贪污行为者的处理的方法，必须事先经市委批准，以免造成偏向。”毛泽东在“必须事先经市委批准”后加括号写了这句话。"}],"contents":[{"id":"153d991cbb","type":"title","text":"在中央关于三反中处理科学家、学者的问题的指示稿上加写的话","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"ca4594d10d"},{"id":"bebd03e3a6","type":"paragraph","text":"有些人须经省委或中央局批准。三","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"ca4594d10d"}],"page":{"id":"460c55050b","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"ca4594d10d","start":497,"end":497}}}},"__N_SSG":true}